cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on the application of convolutional neural networks for object detection and pose estimation in still images, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks for this task also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The task of estimating 3D pose can also be related to robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the evaluation of the proposed approach involves metrics related to multimedia (cs.MM).
